    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hammering tools of modest size, having a handle and relatively large head, usually of wood but sometimes of other materials. Often used to drive another tool, such as a chisel or a gouge.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
